content: Amazing app for those who need lists to help them but find creating lists tedious. Fully featured and well designed. Best productivity tool on this store.
Great stuff! Very useful for organising tasks, great feature set, worth the money.

This app is great! RIP removes the boring and mundane nature of normal task planners and gamifies it to appeal to those of use who need a little zest in their lives. Normally boring things like cleaning, working out, and drinking water can be gamified through RIP and made into a sort of self competition where you will be able to track your statistics of completion and be inclined to continue in order to not fall behind. Overall, RIP is a unique concept made into a simple and easy to use app.
